## Heroku
https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/getting-started-with-python#deploy-the-app

sudo snap install heroku --classic
heroku login
git clone https://github.com/heroku/python-getting-started.git # ez a mintaprojekt
cd python-getting-started
heroku create
git push heroku 'main' #vagyis a fő branzs pl master
heroku ps:scale web=1
heroku open

mashogy:

.
├── app.py
├── requirements.txt
├── setup.sh
└── Procfile

